metadata.name: Meteorite Genesis NFT #1
metadata.description: Meteorite Genesis NFTs are digital arts created with meteorite as the theme.There are a total of 30 NFTs in the Genesis series, each of them is unique. They are specially offered for the attendees of the Meteorite Capital Event on September 15, 2021. Holding Genesis NFT will have rights and benifits from Meteorite Ecosystem, It is also stand for honor and the utmost highly respectable identity.
